result.execSummary:
The defendant Tarray J. Johnson Sr was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Tarray J. Johnson Sr is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Tarray J. Johnson Sr was found guilty of Disorderly Conduct - Domestic Abuse Repeater [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse, Domestic Abuse Repeater], an unclassified felony, Wisconsin Statutes 947.01(1).
  • Tarray J. Johnson Sr was found guilty of Bail Jumping-Misdemeanor, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 946.49(1)(a).
